metadata.name: ATLAS
metadata.description: The first of the Titans I collection, Atlas was the Titan god of astronomy and the revolution of the heavenly constellations, for which Zeus condemned him to bear the heavens upon his shoulders. He was later released from this torment and appointed guardian of the pillars of heaven. Join Atlasâ€™ cause with your Mecha Suit, made just for you, to watch over the metaverse.
